      <p>As a result of extensions to the DICOM standard, the "Modality Worklist CTN" has in the meantime been replaced by a new implementation (application "wlmscpfs") within the <a class="textlink" href="dcmtk.php.en">OFFIS DICOM Toolkit</a>.</p>
